Dion Wired is hosting a Grand Opening Sale at its Sandton store, with many tech items available at reduced prices. The sale will run for 4 days, starting today from 07:00 (29 November to 2 December). The shop – U317C on 83 Rivonia Road, Sandton – will only offer limited deals on a per-customer basis, however, and the deals book states that the specials are limited to one per customer. A selection of the deals are shown below. To see all the deals, visit the Dion Wired website.             